high_descs: Go straight and then right to exit this room, going through the next doorway ahead and approaching the cabinets to the right of the entrance.
Remove the green cloth from the cabinet.
Exit the room the way you came in, then turn right and go into the bathroom.
Wash the cloth in the sink and pick it back up.
Look to the high shelf across from the toilet.
Place the cloth on the shelf.
